title: Southeastern edges Tennessee Tech in 10-inning pitchers duel - crescentcitysports.com
content: Southeastern edges Tennessee Tech in 10-inning pitchers duel  crescentcitysports.com
description: Lions Win Pitcher’s Duel in Extra Innings HAMMOND, La. – The Southeastern Louisiana University baseball team earned its fifth comeback victory of the season Friday in dramatic fashion, defeating red-hot Tennessee Tech, 2-1, in 10 innings at Pat Kenelly Diamond at Alumni Field. Both starting pitchers were dominant, setting the tone for a fast-paced game....
